      <title>IDF部队已经开始在加沙地面运营有限</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/idf-forces-have-begun-limited-ground-operation-in-gaza</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列国防军已开始在加沙地带的中心和南部进行有限的地面行动，目的是扩大安全区并在加沙北部和南部建立部分缓冲区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/idf-forces-have-begun-limited-ground-operation-in-gaza</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 15:21:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院民主党人要求马诺制定职员名单，道德政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/house-democrats-ask-doge-to-produce-staffer-list-ethics-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院民主党人正在敦促唐纳德·特朗普总统政府效率部门，以提高透明度，以解决亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）努力减少政府规模和范围的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/house-democrats-ask-doge-to-produce-staffer-list-ethics-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 15:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将1.75亿美元冻结给宾夕法尼亚州的跨性别运动员</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-freezes-175-million-to-penn-over-transgender-athletes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据白宫快速响应账户X上的一篇文章，特朗普政府已将联邦资金冻结给宾夕法尼亚大学，理由允许跨性别运动员参加妇女体育运动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-freezes-175-million-to-penn-over-transgender-athletes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 14:55:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么Hormuz海峡至关重要，而且有风险的运输</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/strait-of-hormuz-why-the-oil-shipping-route-is-vital-risky</link>
      <description><![CDATA[霍尔木兹海峡是波斯湾河口的狭窄水路，很少远离全球紧张局势的中心。一条主要的运输路线可处理全球石油贸易的26％，密切关注的是中断的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/strait-of-hormuz-why-the-oil-shipping-route-is-vital-risky</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 14:38:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普呼吁弹each法官燃料与法院摊牌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-s-call-for-impeaching-judges-fuels-a-showdown-with-courts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在为他的政府造成了一系列法律损失之后，唐纳德·特朗普总统呼吁弹each联邦法官＆Mdash；以及随后的美国最高法院首席大法官＆Mdash的斥责；为白宫与司法机构之间的加深冲突奠定了基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-s-call-for-impeaching-judges-fuels-a-showdown-with-courts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 14:19:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维科夫说，俄罗斯无人机在普京下令停止之前击中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/witkoff-says-russian-drones-hit-before-putin-ordered-directive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的一位高级顾问否认，俄罗斯违反了一项协议，不攻击乌克兰能源基础设施，并将该协议称为一个突破，可以终止莫斯科的全球隔离，并恢复诸如Nord Stream 2 Pipeline之类的能源项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/witkoff-says-russian-drones-hit-before-putin-ordered-directive</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 14:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡（Netanyahu）紧紧抓住以色列的分歧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/netanyahu-gets-larger-majority-as-israel-strikes-on-gaza-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列说，加沙致命罢工的恢复旨在增加对哈马斯的压力。这也加强了总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡（Benjamin Netanyahu）对权力的控制，并在公众中引起了严重的不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/netanyahu-gets-larger-majority-as-israel-strikes-on-gaza-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 12:32:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫说，特朗普在普京打电话后与Zelenskiy交谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/zelenskiy-says-will-talk-to-trump-on-wednesday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）于周三与乌克兰对话者Volodymyr Zelenskiy开始了电话会谈，这是美国总统与弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）的对话之后的第二天，未能赢得俄罗斯对乌克兰30天停火的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/zelenskiy-says-will-talk-to-trump-on-wednesday</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 10:08:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京将乌克兰休战归于特朗普合作伙伴关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/putin-puts-ukraine-truce-on-ice-in-search-for-trump-partnership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）周二用他的电话与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）打了电话，说美国可能会被俄罗斯＆Mdash扮演。字面上地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/putin-puts-ukraine-truce-on-ice-in-search-for-trump-partnership</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 09:05:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的“贬低”跨性别部队禁令被法官封锁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/trump-s-transgender-troop-ban-blocked-by-judge-during-litigation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名联邦法官暂时阻止了唐纳德·特朗普总统的执行命令的执行，禁止跨性别人民武装部队，认为该指令“浸入了动画”对一个少数群体，并“毫不掩饰地贬低”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/trump-s-transgender-troop-ban-blocked-by-judge-during-litigation</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 22:51:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
